Winux OS GRUB Theme
===================

This theme requires the following image assets to be placed in this directory:

Required Images:
- background.png          - Main background (1920x1080 recommended)
- terminal_box_*.png      - Terminal background (9-part scaling)
- menu_*.png              - Menu background (9-part scaling)
- select_*.png            - Selected item highlight (9-part scaling)
- scrollbar_thumb.png     - Scrollbar thumb
- scrollbar_frame.png     - Scrollbar track
- highlight_*.png         - Progress bar highlight

Optional Icons (32x32 PNG):
- winux.png               - Winux OS boot option icon
- ubuntu.png              - Ubuntu recovery icon
- memtest.png             - Memory test icon
- settings.png            - UEFI settings icon

Color Palette:
- Primary:    #6366f1 (Indigo)
- Secondary:  #8b5cf6 (Purple)
- Background: #1a1a2e (Dark blue)
- Text:       #ffffff (White)
- Muted:      #666666 (Gray)

Installation:
1. Copy this directory to /boot/grub/themes/winux/
2. Add to /etc/default/grub:
   GRUB_THEME="/boot/grub/themes/winux/theme.txt"
3. Run: sudo update-grub
